---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Nous aider" description="Comment soutenir l'Étoile Cycliste Ouvrière de Firminy - Bénévolat, dons et partenariats">
  <div class="pt-20 pb-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-red-50 to-pink-100">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
        Nous aider
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Découvrez comment vous pouvez contribuer au développement de notre club et soutenir la pratique du cyclisme
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <!-- Façons d'aider -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-12 text-center">Comment nous soutenir ?</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <!-- Bénévolat -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
            <div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="p-8">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Bénévolat</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
                Rejoignez notre équipe de bénévoles et participez activement à la vie du club. 
                Votre aide est précieuse pour organiser les événements et encadrer les sorties.
              </p>
              <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6 text-sm text-gray-600">
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                  Encadrement des sorties
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                  Organisation d'événements
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                  Maintenance du matériel
                </li>
              </ul>
              <button class="w-full bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white py-3 px-6 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-colors">
                Devenir bénévole
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Dons -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
            <div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500 to-green-600 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="p-8">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Dons</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
                Vos dons nous permettent d'améliorer notre équipement, d'organiser plus d'événements 
                et de maintenir des tarifs accessibles pour tous nos membres.
              </p>
              <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6 text-sm text-gray-600">
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                  Achat de nouveaux vélos
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                  Équipement de sécurité
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                  Outils d'atelier
                </li>
              </ul>
              <button class="w-full bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700 text-white py-3 px-6 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-colors">
                Faire un don
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Partenariat -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
            <div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-purple-600 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 13.255A23.931 23.931 0 0112 15c-3.183 0-6.22-.62-9-1.745M16 6V4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-4a2 2 0 00-2-2v2m8 0H8m8 0v2a2 2 0 01-2 2H10a2 2 0 01-2-2V6m8 0H8"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="p-8">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Partenariat</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
                Entreprises locales, devenez partenaires de l'ECOF ! Bénéficiez d'une visibilité 
                auprès de notre communauté tout en soutenant le sport local.
              </p>
              <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6 text-sm text-gray-600">
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-purple-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                  Visibilité sur nos supports
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-purple-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                  Événements dédiés
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-purple-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                  Réseau professionnel
                </li>
              </ul>
              <button class="w-full bg-purple-600 hover:bg-purple-700 text-white py-3 px-6 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-colors">
                Devenir partenaire
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Nos besoins actuels -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-12 text-center">Nos besoins actuels</h2>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8">
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Matériel prioritaire</h3>
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
                  <div class="flex items-center">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span class="font-medium">5 vélos enfants</span>
                  </div>
                  <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold">1 500€</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
                  <div class="flex items-center">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span class="font-medium">Casques de sécurité</span>
                  </div>
                  <span class="text-green-600 font-bold">800€</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
                  <div class="flex items-center">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span class="font-medium">Outils d'atelier</span>
                  </div>
                  <span class="text-purple-600 font-bold">600€</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Projets en cours</h3>
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <div class="p-4 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-blue-900 mb-2">Rénovation de l'atelier</h4>
                  <p class="text-blue-700 text-sm mb-2">Modernisation de l'espace de réparation</p>
                  <div class="w-full bg-blue-200 rounded-full h-2">
                    <div class="bg-blue-600 h-2 rounded-full" style="width: 65%"></div>
                  </div>
                  <p class="text-xs text-blue-600 mt-1">65% financé</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="p-4 bg-green-50 rounded-lg">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-green-900 mb-2">Nouveau véhicule de support</h4>
                  <p class="text-green-700 text-sm mb-2">Achat d'un véhicule pour les sorties</p>
                  <div class="w-full bg-green-200 rounded-full h-2">
                    <div class="bg-green-600 h-2 rounded-full" style="width: 30%"></div>
                  </div>
                  <p class="text-xs text-green-600 mt-1">30% financé</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="p-4 bg-purple-50 rounded-lg">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-purple-900 mb-2">École de cyclisme élargie</h4>
                  <p class="text-purple-700 text-sm mb-2">Extension du programme jeunes</p>
                  <div class="w-full bg-purple-200 rounded-full h-2">
                    <div class="bg-purple-600 h-2 rounded-full" style="width: 15%"></div>
                  </div>
                  <p class="text-xs text-purple-600 mt-1">15% financé</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Témoignages -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-12 text-center">Ils nous soutiennent</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1472099645785-5658abf4ff4e?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=100&q=80" 
                   alt="Portrait" class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full mr-4">
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Pierre Martin</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Bénévole depuis 5 ans</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 italic">
              "Aider le club m'apporte autant que ce que je donne. L'esprit d'équipe et la passion partagée 
              font de chaque moment passé avec l'ECOF un vrai plaisir."
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1494790108755-2616b612b786?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=100&q=80" 
                   alt="Portrait" class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full mr-4">
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Marie Dubois</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Cycles Fontainebleau</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 italic">
              "En tant que partenaire, nous sommes fiers de soutenir l'ECOF. C'est un club qui partage 
              nos valeurs et qui fait rayonner le cyclisme dans notre région."
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=100&q=80" 
                   alt="Portrait" class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full mr-4">
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Jean Leroy</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Donateur régulier</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 italic">
              "Mes dons permettent aux jeunes de découvrir le cyclisme dans de bonnes conditions. 
              C'est un investissement dans l'avenir du sport local."
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Contact pour aider -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center text-white">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Prêt à nous aider ?</h2>
        <p class="text-xl mb-8 opacity-90 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Quelle que soit la forme de votre soutien, nous serons ravis de vous accueillir dans notre communauté de supporters.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="mailto:benevoles@ecof-fontainebleau.fr" class="bg-white text-blue-600 hover:bg-gray-100 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-colors">
            Devenir bénévole
          </a>
          <a href="mailto:partenariats@ecof-fontainebleau.fr" class="bg-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-800 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-colors border border-white/30">
            Nous contacter
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>